<br>
On a recent raid to Plane of Fear we were lucky enough to kill the named Gollems who spawn the Iksar Child.  The child has 20hp and is level 1.  The child drops the the Child's Tear which is by far the hardest part of the Shaman Epic.  To spawn the child u have to kill a mob that death touches for 20k hp's.  And fear is not an easy zone to get into as u are immediately attacked upon zone in by mobs that add by the dozen.  In short, Plane of Fear sucks.<br>
<br>
Getting back to Kosko, he joined us on the recent raid.  We killed the named mob and spawned the Iksar Child.  Before anyone could react he disbanded from the raid (to avoid lewt rights), killed the child, lewted the tear, and gated.  He did not have the right to do this.  He is the slime of the earth - there is no excuse for what he did.  It was not a mistake as he knew very well what he was doing.<br>
<br>
Post facto his previous guild has confirmed his slimyness.  Had they warned us sooner he would not have been on the raidor in the guild.<br>
<br>
Please do not help him in any way shape or form.  Do not group with him. And if u feel like it, spam him until he has the courage to do what is right - DELETE YOURSELF!!!! <br>
<br>
Kosko you dont deserve to play this game.  Go join a PvP server and get your just reward.<br>
<br>
If anyone has any information on his Alts - please list.  I dont want to be near this loser ever again.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your help in advance, <br>
Venerable Visn Whiteyes<br>
Exiled Gatekeepers<br>
